precis:
PROHIBITION OF ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS ORDER, 1992, NO. 1 - which prohibits
prospecting and mining on over 600 square miles of land situated in the
Peel River Basin in the Yukon in order to facilitate the settlement of
territorial claims made by the GWICH'IN OF THE MACKENZIE DELTA.
